  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Ensuring rapid and effective distribution of NFIs</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The purpose of this grant is to improve the availability of Non-Food Items (NFIs) and emergency shelter materials for vulnerable populations. This will be achieved by strengthening Save the Children in South Sudan (SCiSS) prepositioning  through investments in infrastructure and personnel. This grant will also ensure that SCiSS keeps a constant focus on the nature and efficiency of its NFI distributions  establishing and maintaining a rigorous accountability mechanism. Finally  coordination will be improved by the presence of additional personnel  who will participate in all national and state-level coordination forums.</narrative>
  </description>
